Git Rebase Aliases

Interactive rebase helpers with autosquash and autostash.

$ [prgm]git frbi[/prgm]                 # Pick parent commit for rebase (uses fzf)
$ [prgm]git apply-fixup[/prgm]          # Rebase to merge-base with master/main

Both commands use [arg]--autosquash[/arg] to automatically apply fixup commits and [arg]--update-refs[/arg] to update dependent branches.

[bold]See also:[/bold] [prgm]git-absorb[/prgm] - automatically creates fixup commits for staged changes.
